                <p>If you were a fan of traversing around in the grass in Grounded, you're probably eager to jump into <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/grounded-2/" data-ref-id="5000-681580">Grounded 2</a> to see what's next in this cooperative survival adventure franchise. With an even larger open world and plenty of new features and mechanics to figure out, this one's all but guaranteed to be a hit for new and returning players. But before you dive in and check everything out, here's what you'll want to know about Grounded 2's cross-play and cross-progression features.</p><h2>Does Grounded 2 have cross-play?</h2><p>If you're eager to tackle the dangerous world of Grounded 2 with friends, but you're concerned that you're on different platforms--don't worry! <strong>Grounded 2 fully supports cross-play across Xbox Series X and PC</strong>, meaning you and your friends can team up regardless of where you enjoy playing your games.</p>



    
